1) Go to Kibana --> Manage your Data under Manage permissions.

2) To create Roles - In Security Tab --> Roles --> Create Roles

3) Provide Role name - follow the naming convention - platformname_permission

4) Provide Index Privileges - Provide the Index name and the required permission and create Role.

5) To create Users - In Security Tab --> Users --> Create Users

6) Provide the Username, Password, Full Name and the required Role and create User.


